      <title>外资回归，印度股市相对于亚洲股市溢价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/indian-stocks-premium-over-asia-hits-record-as-foreigners-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者增持本土股票并减少对区域股票的持仓，印度股市相对于亚洲其他股市的溢价升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/indian-stocks-premium-over-asia-hits-record-as-foreigners-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
